        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to promote the protected cultivation of commercial horticultural crops by providing financial assistance to farmers. The scheme supports greenhouse, shade net, low tunnel, plastic mulching, bird/hail net, and cultivation of vegetables and flowers under polyhouse/shade net house.",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme &amp;quot;Scheme for Promotion of Protected Cultivation of Commercial Horticultural Crops&amp;quot; launched by the Horticulture and Food Processing Department, Government of Madhya Pradesh, aims to promote protected cultivation through providing financial assistance up to 50% of the unit cost to eligible farmers.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - **Financial Assistance:** Eligible farmers are provided a subsidy up to a maximum of 50% of the unit cost.\n<br>\n\n",
